snippet.title: SCP: Site-19. (SCP on mobile)
snippet.description:
*UPDATE* I don't know why this video has no sound. Probably Youtube did something. Next video will be with a sound.
Hello everybody. Currently, I am working on SCP: Site 19.
So the SCP: Site 19 is the mobile game based on SCP Foundation. 
The models & textures are from SCP Containment Breach.
Please support me on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/aidynilyas
So I can use some paid assets, pay for the engine license and work on this project full-time. 
Join discord channel:
https://discord.gg/KNBt7DG
To keep up with events and news!
